features: The super strong magnet design uses 24 N54 magnetic cores, with maximum vertical adsorption force of 8kg on the front, which can securely secure your phone without any risk of falling.
Compatible with iPhone 15, 14, 13, and 12 series, and comes with an iron ring for other phones without magnetic suction function.
With 1/4-20 hole, it can be connected to different devices as needed. Can be used for tripods, direct live streaming tripods, selfie poles, etc.
Unlike traditional tripod Holder , it is a magnetic mount, so you only need one hand and one second to place your phone on it. Supports both horizontal and vertical screens, with 360 ° adjustment.

body.description: If you are looking for a magnet tripod adapter with super strong suction, this will be a good choice. Our magnet adapter is made of 24 N54 magnetic cores (usually only 12 on the market), with a vertical adsorption force of up to 8kg on the front. It can firmly fix your phone on the tripod or selfie stick without the risk of detachment.
